# MarketingOS — Cursor Rules
# Place this file at the repo root as .cursorrules
# Cursor reads this before every suggestion in this project.

---

## Project Identity

This is MarketingOS — an AI-powered marketing platform built on Next.js 15, Prisma, PostgreSQL, Auth.js v5, TanStack Query v5, and Tailwind CSS v4.

Milestone 1 is complete. The scaffold, auth, and brand creation are live.
Milestone 2 (Brand Brain full form + context serialiser) is in progress.
Do not invent architecture. Follow what exists.

---

## Folder Structure — Strict

```
src/
  app/
    (auth)/           ← unauthenticated pages (login)
    (dashboard)/      ← all protected pages live here
      layout.tsx      ← SERVER component — fetches brands, auth check
    api/
      auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts
  components/
    layout/           ← Sidebar, BrandSwitcher (receive props, no fetching)
    ui/               ← reusable primitives
  lib/
    auth.ts           ← NextAuth config only
    db.ts             ← Prisma singleton only
    nav.ts            ← NAV_ITEMS config
    utils.ts          ← cn(), slugify(), getInitials()
    ai/               ← AI provider abstraction (M3+)
      provider.ts     ← ONLY place that imports AI SDKs
  providers/
    index.tsx         ← QueryClientProvider
  types/
    index.ts
  middleware.ts
```

Any file you create must fit this structure. If it doesn't fit cleanly, ask before creating.

