## Quick Lookups

| Task | Where |
|---|---|
| Add a sidebar nav item | `src/lib/nav.ts` → `NAV_ITEMS` array |
| Protect a new route | Already protected by middleware — add to `PUBLIC_ROUTES` to unprotect |
| Add a new Zod schema | Co-locate in the `actions.ts` for that feature |
| Change the brand accent colour | It's set as inline style on the dashboard layout root div |
| Add a new AI employee | `src/lib/ai/employees/[employee-name].ts` (M3) |
| Add a Prisma table | Check full schema doc → write migration → run `npm run db:migrate` |
